hps_pre_tips_details.content: 1. Non-instant betting method with conditions to be valid
2. Only for specified matches & market types
3. Immediate deduction after booking submission, Immediate refund after cancellation/failure
4. The maximum number of inPlay bets for a single match is 10
5. When the default booked odds are the current odds, it’s considered normal betting
6. 'Booking' means the bet is booked successful but not yet valid
7. When the market odds reach the booked odds, the system will automatically process the bets

list.punish_details: Booking markets are settled on a points system. Red Cards equal 2 points, while Yellow Cards equal 1 point. The maximum points any player can accumulate is 3.
